{
  "id": "5c138dfc47fabc0014385470",
  "title": "観る訓練",
  "created": 1544785430,
  "updated": 1544791399,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5c138dfc47fabc0014385470",
      "text": "観る訓練",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1544785430,
      "updated": 1544785439
    },
    {
      "id": "5c138e1eaff09e0000c61c81",
      "text": "[瞑想]を、無心になるとか雑念を消すとか「止める」のメタファーで考えがち。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1544785439,
      "updated": 1544791211
    },
    {
      "id": "5c138e45aff09e0000c61c84",
      "text": "止めるは行動。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1544785478,
      "updated": 1544791215
    },
    {
      "id": "5c138e4aaff09e0000c61c85",
      "text": "観察する訓練。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1544785483,
      "updated": 1544791329
    },
    {
      "id": "5c138e5daff09e0000c61c86",
      "text": "観察者としての自分と観察対象としての自分をまず分離させる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1544785502,
      "updated": 1544791343
    },
    {
      "id": "5c138e6aaff09e0000c61c87",
      "text": "主客分離。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1544785515,
      "updated": 1544791346
    },
    {
      "id": "5c13a532aff09e00000cd7b4",
      "text": "次に分離した状態を保ちながら一体に戻る。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1544791346,
      "updated": 1544791358
    },
    {
      "id": "5c138eb5aff09e0000c61c88",
      "text": "主客一体。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1544785590,
      "updated": 1544791361
    },
    {
      "id": "5c13a543aff09e00000cd7b5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1544791363,
      "updated": 1544791363
    },
    {
      "id": "5c138ebaaff09e0000c61c89",
      "text": "感情に身をまかせるのではなく感情を発している自分を観察する。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1544785595,
      "updated": 1544791369
    },
    {
      "id": "5c13a551aff09e00000cd7b6",
      "text": "今自分が感情を発している状態であるか、そうでない状態かを識別する訓練をする。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1544791378,
      "updated": 1544791393
    },
    {
      "id": "5c138ed3aff09e0000c61c8a",
      "text": "この訓練によって他人の感情の発生にも気付きやすくなる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1544785620,
      "updated": 1544791395
    },
    {
      "id": "5c138ee4aff09e0000c61c8b",
      "text": "感情には原因がある。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1544785637,
      "updated": 1544791396
    },
    {
      "id": "5c138eefaff09e0000c61c8c",
      "text": "因果。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1544785648,
      "updated": 1544791399
    },
    {
      "id": "5c138ef2aff09e0000c61c8d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1544785650,
      "updated": 1544785650
    },
    {
      "id": "5c138e2baff09e0000c61c82",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1544785451,
      "updated": 1544785451
    }
  ]
}